text: Igor Pastukhovich (born 14 November 1966) is a Soviet former cyclist. He competed in the team time trial at the 1992 Summer Olympics for the Unified Team. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of the Unified Team Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
